Name: Rabbit Maze
About the game: This is a maze game. In the level mode, there are fifteen maps available 1-10 levels are incremental random maps 11-15 15levels are non random maps,Each map has its own style, but the last map may require some different thinking to pass In the endless mode You can choose the size of the map according to your preference and the configuration of your computer Maybe you can choose a custom 2x2 map and finish it instantly Maybe you can choose a map of 10000x10000 and lose yourself in it for a lifetime If you are tired If you want to stay away from conflict You can choose Zen mode The main difference between Zen mode and endless mode is that you observe rather than participate You can customize a map and see how AI can go out through its own less intelligent mind Maybe you'll find In life We're like the AI that can't walk out of the maze
